  ],
  "confidence_tier": "high",
  "industry_note": "Polycarbonate grades by molecular weight (MW): • Low MW (Lexan 101R 12 MFR, Makrolon 2407): σy 65 / E 2.4 / Tmax 115°C — injection molding ease, thin-wall • Standard MW (Lexan 121R 9 MFR, Makrolon 2858): σy 62-65 / Tmax 115-127°C — general purpose • High MW (Lexan EXL 3 MFR, Makrolon 3108): σy 67 / E 2.4 / Tmax 127°C — tough grade, optical, riot shield, bullet-resistant glazing 낮은 MW → easier 가공, lower 강도. 광 투과 90%, refractive index 1.586.",
